I’ve got a plausible root cause: wrong ring ordering. I’m patching a tighter strategy set around that.
Plan update
The failure is consistent with signing the five-member ring in the wrong seat order. I’m updating the verifier to try the historical replay first, then generate fresh LSAG transcripts for the two plausible ring orderings while keeping the same deposit→withdrawStart→withdrawStep→withdrawFinal exploit path.
